Description: SecuBox Unified UI Manager
 Manages the SecuBox user interface with automatic mode selection
 and graceful fallback support.
 .
 Features:
  - KUI: Kiosk UI mode (X11 + Chromium fullscreen)
  - TUI: Terminal UI mode (Textual-based console)
  - Console: Fallback to standard getty login
  - Automatic hypervisor detection (VirtualBox, QEMU/KVM, VMware)
  - Per-hypervisor graphics optimization
  - Modular debug system with 6 verbosity levels
  - Health monitoring with automatic fallback on failure
 .
 This package is part of the SecuBox security appliance.
